1
00:00:06,040 --> 00:00:08,667
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,667 --> 00:00:12,122
♫ Time has made me whimsical ♫

3
00:00:12,122 --> 00:00:18,315
♫ I want to seize the day And put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,315 --> 00:00:24,541
♫ I want to go back in time To do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,541 --> 00:00:31,062
♫ Don't say goodbye And don't glaze. All the lights are lit up ♫

6
00:00:31,062 --> 00:00:36,048
♫ We are always looking forward
to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:36,048 --> 00:00:43,348
♫ And overlooking the best arrangements
just by our sides ♫

8
00:00:43,348 --> 00:00:48,372
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,372 --> 00:00:49,885
♫ BE YOUR LIGHT ♫

10
00:00:49,885 --> 00:00:55,648
♫ No doubt you're irreplaceable ♫

11
00:00:55,648 --> 00:01:02,248
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,248 --> 00:01:08,415
♫ You are my incredible highlight ♫

13
00:01:08,415 --> 00:01:11,802
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:20,130 --> 00:01:23,696
Good morning, Tiger. Hello.

15
00:01:25,110 --> 00:01:29,000
We hung out all night and watched the stars together, right?

16
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:33,040
We're brothers now. Come on. Let's shake hands.

17
00:01:35,010 --> 00:01:38,882
So aloof. I can shake your foot too.

18
00:01:38,882 --> 00:01:42,571
Hello. Good boy.

19
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:48,154
You're not scared anymore?

20
00:01:48,750 --> 00:01:53,058
I was never scared. He's much easier going than you.

21
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,700
Are you going to train?

22
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:05,440
Gao Bin, time to train!

23
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,980
Gao Bin!

24
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:14,979
Wake up! What time is it? Geez.

25
00:02:15,970 --> 00:02:17,739
Are you still sleeping?

26
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:29,360
What's wrong?

27
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,177
Check it out yourself.

28
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:04,060
Beibei, have some peanuts.

29
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,240
No.

30
00:03:06,690 --> 00:03:08,880
Meng, you have some.

31
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,560
How did it go last night?

32
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:18,500
It was all right.

33
00:03:19,230 --> 00:03:23,959
I drank some grape juice and I had some stewed pork shoulder.

34
00:03:23,959 --> 00:03:26,691
After that, I took photos with the villagers and gave them my autograph.

35
00:03:26,691 --> 00:03:29,339
In the end, I even sang a song.

36
00:03:30,230 --> 00:03:32,860
You had quite a splendid day.

37
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:35,539
What happened to you girls?

38
00:03:35,539 --> 00:03:39,739
Beibei and I snuck out and my mom found out.

39
00:03:43,060 --> 00:03:46,919
Mi Jia and Beibei had a fight.

40
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:48,320
And also Mr. Gao.

41
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:52,880
He got drunk again last night and couldn't wake up for Xiaowen's training.

42
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:55,120
Gao Yang is still mad at him.

43
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:59,231
Mr. Gao really made a mistake this time.

44
00:03:59,231 --> 00:04:01,031
Stop the bus, Sir.

45
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,536
Gao Yang!

46
00:04:08,536 --> 00:04:09,936
Gao Yang!

47
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:12,260
Gao Yang!

48
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:16,439
Look at him! That's how Gao Bin is. How can you ask me to trust him? How can I trust him?

49
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:18,339
All right, get back on the bus first. Everyone's waiting.

50
00:04:18,339 --> 00:04:20,446
I don't want to take the same bus with him.

51
00:04:20,446 --> 00:04:23,119
Well, if you don't trust him, can you trust me?

52
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,260
Trust you on what?

53
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:30,020
I said I can seize this opportunity to get into the national competition and I'll do that.

54
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:34,879
But... I just can't stand him.

55
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:39,979
I know. If you can't stand others, can you take care of your own matter first?

56
00:04:39,979 --> 00:04:43,079
Didn't you say you want to improve by 30 ranks in the final exam? Can you do that?

57
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:46,380
Of course, I can. I'm not Gao Bin.

58
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:51,660
Fine, I'll wait and see. Let's go.

59
00:04:54,170 --> 00:04:56,560
All right, let's go back now. Let's go.

60
00:04:56,560 --> 00:05:01,402
[Episode 18: Thorn of Disappointment]

61
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:30,579
Third Uncle, what kind of liquor is this?

62
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:40,239
Xiaowen, time to train.

63
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:47,797
Oh, no!

64
00:05:49,550 --> 00:05:53,900
Xiaowen, I... I... I'm sorry. I shouldn't be drinking.

65
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:58,039
Third Uncle told me w-we would just have two cups. T-Then it turned into f-four cups...

66
00:05:58,039 --> 00:06:02,079
It's okay, Mr. Gao. It's all right.

67
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:05,580
Xiaowen, are you going to train now? I'll go with you.

68
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:09,760
Let's start the second phase of our training. W-Wait for me.

69
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:13,700
W-Where are my shoes? Where are they?

70
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:17,540
Where did my shoes go? I'll be ready soon, Xiaowen.

71
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:20,039
That's all right, Mr. Gao.

72
00:06:20,039 --> 00:06:21,360
I'll be ready soon.

73
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:26,020
I already know how to train. I can just go by myself.

74
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:51,779
Mr. Gao, I'm really fine. You don't have to worry about me.

75
00:06:51,779 --> 00:06:55,312
Xiaowen, that day...

76
00:06:55,312 --> 00:06:59,739
Third Uncle was talking to me about my divorce with Gao Yang's mom.

77
00:06:59,739 --> 00:07:02,520
I just felt really upset.

78
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:07,399
As I felt upset, I j-just had a bit too much to drink. I-I'm so sorry.

79
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:11,799
Why don't we go train?

80
00:07:11,799 --> 00:07:16,339
That's all right. You should check on Gao Yang.

81
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,119
Yang, Yang!

82
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:56,380
Daddy, I made a mistake.

83
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,491
Should you be mopping the floor?

84
00:07:59,491 --> 00:08:02,019
- I'll go study, then.
- Stop!

85
00:08:02,650 --> 00:08:06,740
You've been out for two days. Isn't it too late to study now?

86
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:07,820
Then I'll mop the floor.

87
00:08:07,820 --> 00:08:09,320
Come back here.

88
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:17,179
All right, don't you love to play? Go play. Play all you want.

89
00:08:17,179 --> 00:08:21,280
Play until you're eighteen and I'll disown you. Does that sound good?

90
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:24,079
Dad, don't! I was wrong.

91
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:28,879
I shouldn't run out and I shouldn't leave Doudou home alone!

92
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:31,760
Doudou is none of your business!

93
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:36,660
He gets perfect scores on every test! What about you?

94
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:41,400
I... Well... I can surely improve by 30 ranks in the final exam.

95
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,559
That's what you said.

96
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:50,100
If you can't achieve that, this summer vacation will be tough for you.

97
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:54,479
Don't worry, Dad! I will study hard for sure!

98
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,721
Hello?

99
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,740
Hello?

100
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,807
Who are you?

101
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:22,079
S-Say something.

102
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:27,139
Who is it?

103
00:09:27,139 --> 00:09:29,269
I-I don't know.

104
00:09:29,269 --> 00:09:32,660
T-That person called a-and didn't say anything.

105
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:39,160
Jia, do you think Beibei called to apologize but she was too embarrassed to do it?

106
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:41,400
You should take the initiative,

107
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,540
right?

108
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:52,660
All right, let me say something before the end of class.

109
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:56,645
We've been implementing the class distribution for half a semester.

110
00:09:56,645 --> 00:09:59,020
I know some of you have complaints.

111
00:09:59,020 --> 00:10:03,500
You think we have the elite class, the other classes are inferior.

112
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:06,561
That's not the case. That's not the school's intention.

113
00:10:06,561 --> 00:10:09,819
The school's intention is to implement targeted learning programs

114
00:10:09,819 --> 00:10:12,499
so you can all go to college, right?

115
00:10:12,499 --> 00:10:16,720
Let's all take this chance to prove yourselves, okay?

116
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:22,159
Okay!

117
00:10:23,419 --> 00:10:25,384
Pull yourselves together, right?

118
00:10:25,384 --> 00:10:29,079
Try to get a good score and maybe our class will be the elite class.

119
00:10:29,079 --> 00:10:31,067
Good luck! Class dismissed.

120
00:10:31,067 --> 00:10:34,199
Mr. Wu, I don't understand this problem.

121
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,693
Mr. Wu is such a bold thinker.

122
00:10:39,693 --> 00:10:44,579
He wants to turn Class 3 into the elite class? Are all the other classes not taking the exam?

123
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:49,069
That's mainly because the students in our class are so disappointing.

124
00:10:49,069 --> 00:10:53,340
If all of you are as smart and hardworking as I am,

125
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:55,900
we would have been the elite class a long time ago.

126
00:10:55,900 --> 00:10:57,980
Yeah, right.

127
00:10:57,980 --> 00:10:59,639
You're quite confident.

128
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:03,240
Of course. When have you seen me this serious before?

129
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:07,160
I'll move up 30 ranks this time. Next time, I'll be in the elite class.

130
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,799
If you really make it into the elite class,

131
00:11:12,299 --> 00:11:14,539
I'll play video games with you every day.

132
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,539
That's what you said.

133
00:11:16,539 --> 00:11:20,099
Prepared to lose. Practice your skills of—

134
00:11:20,099 --> 00:11:21,500
What are you doing?

135
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,500
Lie detection.

136
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:24,719
Your pulse is beating pretty fast.

137
00:11:24,719 --> 00:11:27,719
Go away. I'm so worried.

138
00:11:27,719 --> 00:11:29,939
All right,

139
00:11:29,939 --> 00:11:32,219
there's another one over there.

140
00:11:32,219 --> 00:11:37,060
If you two can combine your scores, you can certainly make it into the elite class.

141
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:38,640
Good luck.

142
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:56,059
What are you doing? Enough with those useless efforts.

143
00:11:56,059 --> 00:12:02,859
What should I do then? If I can't move up 30 ranks, I'll be doomed.

144
00:12:05,310 --> 00:12:07,459
Let's go talk outside.

145
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:12,000
Let's talk.

146
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,500
"The road to Shu is hard..."
(T/N: reference to a poetry by Li Bai)

147
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,740
"Climb..."

148
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:22,199
"Alas! The height, the staggering height!"

149
00:12:22,199 --> 00:12:25,480
"The wind so swift, the sky so high, apes wail and cry."

150
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:30,560
- "The road to Shu is so steep, steeper than the sky. "
- "The boundless forest sheds its leaves..."

151
00:12:31,260 --> 00:12:32,519
Enough, hurry up.

152
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,200
Be serious.

153
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,679
Do you know what I'm thinking?

154
00:12:44,679 --> 00:12:48,940
I guess you might be thinking about what I'm thinking.

155
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:56,240
With our own abilities, can we move up 30 ranks?

156
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:59,679
If I can do that, why are we chatting now?

157
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:07,400
What I'm about to say requires a lot of courage.

158
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:11,400
I have nothing in here besides courage.

159
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:14,760
We have to conquer this final exam!

160
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:17,280
- That's more like it!
- Oh, my goodness!

161
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,539
That's the vigor I'm looking for!

162
00:13:20,523 --> 00:13:22,000
- Good luck!
- Good luck!

163
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,360
It's great to have a goal!

164
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,340
- It's a great thing!
- Yes.

165
00:13:24,340 --> 00:13:27,060
- Conquer it!
- Conquer it!

166
00:13:28,130 --> 00:13:29,999
Oh, my goodness.

167
00:13:32,130 --> 00:13:35,459
Come on, it's time to prove our friendship.

168
00:13:52,830 --> 00:13:55,140
If we want to conquer the exam,

169
00:13:55,140 --> 00:14:01,200
we need unity, courage, and firm execution.

170
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:22,039
[The second examination room]

171
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:25,080
We might be split up in different exam places.

172
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:28,880
But one of us would meet one of our own.

173
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:31,400
The one who meets our own people

174
00:14:31,879 --> 00:14:36,420
would need to bring out the precious answers.

175
00:15:14,759 --> 00:15:17,000
The exam is merciless.

176
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:22,439
But the invigilators are merciful.

177
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:26,139
Teacher.

178
00:15:26,139 --> 00:15:27,559
I have a stomachache.
[English Exam, duration: 120 minutes]

179
00:15:27,559 --> 00:15:29,180
Go on. Come back soon.

180
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:31,420
Thank you, teacher.

181
00:15:33,020 --> 00:15:34,959
It hurts so bad.

182
00:15:39,539 --> 00:15:43,700
Knowledge shouldn't be the shackles to progress.

183
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:49,860
I call this plan "Operation Progress".

184
00:16:28,170 --> 00:16:32,219
Check your work. Hurry up. Twenty more minutes to go.

185
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:43,280
What happened?

186
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:45,459
I have a nosebleed, Mr. Wu.

187
00:16:46,835 --> 00:16:48,795
Go put some cold water on it.

188
00:17:19,399 --> 00:17:21,860
Where did you put it?

189
00:17:27,490 --> 00:17:29,199
What happened?

190
00:17:31,450 --> 00:17:33,596
I'm a bit dizzy from losing too much blood.

191
00:17:33,596 --> 00:17:35,396
Can you still finish the exam?

192
00:17:35,396 --> 00:17:38,459
Yes, I can. I can persist.

193
00:17:38,459 --> 00:17:40,959
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

194
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:46,500
- Maybe you should go to the infirmary.
- No, that's okay.

195
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:49,620
This way. Where are you going?
[Grade 11 Class 2]

196
00:17:59,110 --> 00:18:01,019
No, hurry up!

197
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:03,567
Where are the answers?

198
00:18:03,567 --> 00:18:07,459
- You didn't get the answers?
- No. Did you put it there or not?

199
00:18:07,459 --> 00:18:12,700
That's nonsense! I gave you the only copy of the answers. I didn't even copy the answers myself.

200
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:16,200
I looked for it for so long and didn't find anything. If you put it there, where did the answers go?

201
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,019
How would I know?

202
00:18:19,210 --> 00:18:22,340
Did the teachers find out?

203
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:24,059
That can't be.

204
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:26,939
Gao Yang, why are you so dumb?

205
00:18:26,939 --> 00:18:29,159
I gave the only copy of the answers right to you and you still didn't get it.

206
00:18:29,159 --> 00:18:31,100
Is it because I'm dumb?

207
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:32,680
Were you followed?

208
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:35,780
No way. I looked left and right and even behind me after I came out of the exam room.

209
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:38,900
No one was there. I came out of the exam room alone.

210
00:18:38,900 --> 00:18:41,028
Oh, no.

211
00:18:41,028 --> 00:18:45,480
While I waited for your answers, I just drew and scribbled in the back.

212
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:49,119
Me too. I did even worse than last time.

213
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:55,479
How did you do on the exam?

214
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:05,219
Pretty good.

215
00:19:05,219 --> 00:19:07,740
- What about you?
- Pretty good.

216
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:09,540
What about you? How did you do?

217
00:19:09,540 --> 00:19:11,760
I didn't do very well.

218
00:19:12,450 --> 00:19:14,680
This exam is pretty hard.

219
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:17,600
Well, we just made up answers on those hard questions.

220
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:19,000
Exactly.

221
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:22,168
Well, which problem did we get to just now?

222
00:19:22,168 --> 00:19:24,259
How did you answer that big question?

223
00:19:24,259 --> 00:19:26,259
I don't know how to answer any big questions.

224
00:19:28,390 --> 00:19:31,820
- This is how I solved it. Let's go. Didn't the teacher tell us in class?
- Exactly.

225
00:19:31,820 --> 00:19:34,395
"Odd numbers reverse, even numbers remain the same. Plus or minus signs depends on the quadrant."
(T/N: tricks to geometry)

226
00:19:34,395 --> 00:19:36,140
"Odd numbers reverse, even numbers remain the same. Plus or minus signs depends on the quadrant."

227
00:19:36,140 --> 00:19:37,320
- That's right.
- Is that how he taught us?

228
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:39,499
- Yes.
- Didn't he say one to two to radical three?

229
00:19:39,499 --> 00:19:41,580
- Isn't that the Pythagorean theorem?
- Yes, the Pythagorean Theorem.

230
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:43,359
Hurry up.

231
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:47,839
Xiaowen, do you know what this means?

232
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:53,500
Maybe it's not... Is this right?

233
00:20:05,219 --> 00:20:07,119
What do you mean by this?

234
00:20:07,119 --> 00:20:08,839
I quit. You can have them all.

235
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:10,739
I can have them all?

236
00:20:15,119 --> 00:20:20,640
Let me tell you, a few days ago, my wife yelled at me.

237
00:20:21,142 --> 00:20:22,525
Beibei wasn't home.

238
00:20:22,525 --> 00:20:24,957
Doudou was about to drink beer.

239
00:20:24,957 --> 00:20:27,919
She said he learned it from me and asked me to throw out all my alcohol. Did you know that?

240
00:20:27,919 --> 00:20:29,372
Do you want them or not?

241
00:20:29,372 --> 00:20:31,294
Do you want to cause a family conflict?

242
00:20:31,294 --> 00:20:33,154
I'll throw them away if you don't want them.

243
00:20:51,459 --> 00:20:52,959
When did you buy these?

244
00:20:54,179 --> 00:20:56,499
I saved them from the wedding.

245
00:20:56,499 --> 00:20:57,559
Have you opened it?

246
00:20:57,559 --> 00:20:59,580
It's new.

247
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:03,990
Why don't we try it?

248
00:21:07,419 --> 00:21:09,980
You drink it if you want. Don't bring me along.

249
00:21:11,939 --> 00:21:15,920
You're making quite an effort for Xiaowen. You even quit drinking?

250
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:19,279
I can't drink anymore.

251
00:21:19,279 --> 00:21:22,200
I'm over forty years old. I have to pull myself together.

252
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:27,200
Otherwise, the kids will look down upon me.

253
00:21:31,908 --> 00:21:36,839
I'm going away for the weekend. Watch the kids for me.

254
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,739
Where are you going?

255
00:21:38,739 --> 00:21:40,620
Stay out of it.

256
00:21:46,882 --> 00:21:50,602
[No. 3 Tian Yuan Staff Accommodation]

257
00:21:53,475 --> 00:21:56,419
Come on. The dumplings are ready.

258
00:21:56,419 --> 00:21:58,279
They are boiling hot.

259
00:22:00,259 --> 00:22:03,940
You're still drinking? You don't want your health anymore?

260
00:22:03,940 --> 00:22:05,000
Start eating.

261
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:07,720
I drink a little bit to soften the blood vessels.

262
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:12,319
Besides, Bin already quit drinking. It's such a waste to throw them out.

263
00:22:14,060 --> 00:22:18,459
Don't doubt it, Gao Yang. Your dad really quit drinking this time.

264
00:22:18,459 --> 00:22:20,439
He's serious every time.

265
00:22:21,132 --> 00:22:22,932
Eat some dumplings.

266
00:22:23,979 --> 00:22:27,299
What are you doing? Do you want to die?

267
00:22:31,910 --> 00:22:35,240
How is it? Are my pickled cabbage dumplings tasty?

268
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,499
It's very delicious.

269
00:22:36,499 --> 00:22:39,819
Auntie Chang, how did you make the filling?

270
00:22:39,819 --> 00:22:42,820
Let me tell you, I do have a trick for making this filling.

271
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:44,680
You have to add more Sichuan pepper water and scallion and ginger water.

272
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:48,200
Then, use the chopsticks to stir it with all your strength until the filling gradually

273
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:51,880
rises up before you wrap it. That way, it will be tasty.

274
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,340
Learn from her.

275
00:22:53,340 --> 00:22:57,719
Rise up? Xiaowen was just being polite. You're really teaching him?

276
00:22:57,719 --> 00:23:01,100
How about this? You should come teach a class in school.

277
00:23:01,100 --> 00:23:03,640
What's wrong with you? I just didn't want you to drink.

278
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:05,879
What's with the nonsense?

279
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:10,760
Gao Yang, eat more. Your dad will come back tomorrow.

280
00:23:11,519 --> 00:23:12,559
That's right.

281
00:23:12,559 --> 00:23:14,939
I should go cook more for you. You can take them home with you.

282
00:23:14,939 --> 00:23:17,219
- Thank you, Auntie Chang.
- Thank you Aunt Juan.

283
00:23:17,219 --> 00:23:19,019
You're welcome.

284
00:23:24,319 --> 00:23:25,939
Eat, Principal Jin.

285
00:23:25,939 --> 00:23:27,439
It's delicious.

286
00:23:30,019 --> 00:23:35,120
Well, how did you guys do on the final exam?

287
00:23:40,278 --> 00:23:41,480
It's all right.

288
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:44,079
Xiaowen is fine for sure.

289
00:23:44,079 --> 00:23:47,240
What I mean is, what about the other two?

290
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,580
This ham is really good.

291
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:50,680
Eat some more.

292
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:53,000
What about you two?

293
00:23:56,259 --> 00:23:58,492
I'm all right.

294
00:23:58,492 --> 00:24:03,380
What do you mean you're all right? Can you move up 30 ranks?

295
00:24:17,274 --> 00:24:19,720
She must've failed the exam!

296
00:24:28,172 --> 00:24:32,040
Well... It's okay, Principal Jin. I'll make her study.

297
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:33,259
Eat the dumplings.

298
00:24:33,259 --> 00:24:35,780
You should study hard first.

299
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:42,660
Doudou, eat slowly.

300
00:25:00,177 --> 00:25:02,690
Runner-up Gao!

301
00:25:02,690 --> 00:25:05,480
That happened so many years ago. Why are you still bringing it up?

302
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:08,380
Come on. Take a seat.

303
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:11,199
Sit down. Don't move.

304
00:25:11,199 --> 00:25:12,820
Champion Zhang.

305
00:25:12,820 --> 00:25:17,159
I can tell you're still very handsome after so many years.

306
00:25:17,159 --> 00:25:19,359
Take a seat.

307
00:25:20,947 --> 00:25:23,759
Well, why did you come to Linyang?

308
00:25:23,759 --> 00:25:25,600
- Let's talk over lunch.
- Okay.

309
00:25:25,600 --> 00:25:29,159
Waiter, serve the hot dishes. Drink some water.

310
00:25:31,540 --> 00:25:34,520
Auntie Chang Juan's dumplings are so delicious.

311
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:36,580
Did you learn the recipe she just told you?

312
00:25:36,580 --> 00:25:41,119
I'm telling you, I want to see the same dumplings tomorrow.

313
00:25:42,176 --> 00:25:44,496
Is there anything you want to tell me?

314
00:25:47,659 --> 00:25:49,399
I told you already.

315
00:25:49,399 --> 00:25:51,119
Learn to make it.

316
00:25:52,319 --> 00:25:54,019
Think again.

317
00:26:01,267 --> 00:26:02,760
It's time to study.

318
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:05,140
How did you do on this exam?

319
00:26:12,544 --> 00:26:14,544
It's all right.

320
00:26:14,544 --> 00:26:17,699
Why is Beibei so sad?

321
00:26:17,699 --> 00:26:19,353
Oh, Beibei.

322
00:26:19,353 --> 00:26:23,299
Beibei... Well, Beibei... She...

323
00:26:23,299 --> 00:26:26,240
She didn't do as well as I did this time.

324
00:26:26,725 --> 00:26:30,960
Well, I'll go comfort her. Don't come in here.

325
00:26:40,723 --> 00:26:43,580
Beibei, how is it going? Are you okay?

326
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:46,620
I'm doomed!

327
00:26:46,620 --> 00:26:48,520
No, no, don't cry.

328
00:26:48,520 --> 00:26:54,359
Well, if your dad beats you up, I-I'll take the beating for you.

329
00:26:57,000 --> 00:27:00,080
I want to die!

330
00:27:00,080 --> 00:27:04,030
No, calm down, Beibei. Well...

331
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:07,238
I-I-I'll go change the score for you.

332
00:27:07,238 --> 00:27:09,038
How?

333
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:16,440
I-I-I'll go steal the exam papers. I-I'll come over later.

334
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:19,919
After that, I'll steal the key to your dad's office.

335
00:27:19,919 --> 00:27:24,319
Gao Yang, you're the best. Come upstairs soon.

336
00:27:24,319 --> 00:27:27,060
I'm not going to steal the exam papers with you. Over.

337
00:27:27,060 --> 00:27:29,906
You don't have to go. I'll go by myself.

338
00:27:32,811 --> 00:27:36,239
Didn't I tell you not to come in here?

339
00:27:50,039 --> 00:27:51,860
Well,

340
00:27:51,860 --> 00:27:53,660
Over.

341
00:28:17,336 --> 00:28:18,936
Xiaowen,

342
00:28:19,699 --> 00:28:23,199
this... where did you get that?

343
00:28:35,540 --> 00:28:39,640
This... This seems like Beibei's handwriting.

344
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:42,380
This kid, how can she cheat? I'll go put some sense into her.

345
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:44,180
Sure.

346
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:46,420
I'll go talk to Principal Jin too.

347
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:48,279
I was wrong.

348
00:28:49,373 --> 00:28:51,580
For what?

349
00:28:51,580 --> 00:28:53,639
I shouldn't cheat.

350
00:28:56,303 --> 00:29:00,820
- If I didn't find out this time, would you do it again next time?
- No.

351
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:04,739
If you succeed next time, would you keep doing this in the future?

352
00:29:09,231 --> 00:29:13,440
I... I was just trying to make you happy.

353
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:16,359
I promised you I would move up by 30 ranks.

354
00:29:16,359 --> 00:29:18,479
Do you know what you're talking about?

355
00:29:20,919 --> 00:29:22,893
I wanted you to work hard, not cheat!

356
00:29:22,893 --> 00:29:24,844
It doesn't matter if you tried and didn't improve!

357
00:29:24,844 --> 00:29:27,284
I don't want the grades you get from cheating!

358
00:29:30,894 --> 00:29:32,794
I'm sorry, Xiaowen.

359
00:29:39,022 --> 00:29:42,620
I don't have much else to say. It's up to you.

360
00:29:55,822 --> 00:30:00,000
Anyway, that's the situation.

361
00:30:00,061 --> 00:30:01,654
Zhang,

362
00:30:01,654 --> 00:30:07,580
we have been friends for so long, can you do me this favor?

363
00:30:07,580 --> 00:30:11,300
I knew there was a catch when you asked me to lunch.

364
00:30:11,300 --> 00:30:15,039
What are you talking about? We haven't seen each other for a long time.

365
00:30:15,039 --> 00:30:16,659
I miss you.

366
00:30:16,659 --> 00:30:19,859
While I'm here, you can help me at the same time.

367
00:30:19,859 --> 00:30:21,759
You miss me?

368
00:30:21,759 --> 00:30:26,080
You haven't contacted me for so long after we graduated. Now you're asking me for a favor when you see me?

369
00:30:27,870 --> 00:30:31,359
You know about my situation.

370
00:30:31,359 --> 00:30:34,119
I got a divorce and I've been raising a child on my own.

371
00:30:34,119 --> 00:30:37,699
I have no money or anything else.

372
00:30:37,699 --> 00:30:42,919
Look at you. You're the coach of the provincial team and living a glamorous life.

373
00:30:42,919 --> 00:30:45,094
I see you on TV all the time.

374
00:30:45,094 --> 00:30:47,119
All right, all right.

375
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:50,740
This is not an easy task.

376
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:52,900
I wouldn't ask you if it's easy.

377
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:55,297
All right, I'll think about it.

378
00:30:55,297 --> 00:30:56,997
Okay.

379
00:30:57,990 --> 00:31:01,300
- Let's talk over drinks.
- Fine, drink whatever you want.

380
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:07,860
I won't be drinking.

381
00:31:07,860 --> 00:31:09,760
What's going on?

382
00:31:10,990 --> 00:31:12,697
I quit.

383
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:20,080
So, you're asking me for a favor and you quit drinking?

384
00:31:21,170 --> 00:31:24,799
- Then I can't eat anymore.
- Don't, don't.

385
00:31:25,730 --> 00:31:27,338
Are you going to drink or not?

386
00:32:58,170 --> 00:32:59,879
Mr. Gao.

387
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:04,560
Mr. Gao.

388
00:33:05,930 --> 00:33:07,939
Mr. Gao.

389
00:33:07,939 --> 00:33:09,679
Mr. Gao!

390
00:33:19,970 --> 00:33:23,539
Didn't you say you quit drinking? What's going on here?

391
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:35,479
Xiaowen,

392
00:33:35,479 --> 00:33:37,182
I...

393
00:33:37,800 --> 00:33:40,319
I'm sorry.

394
00:33:41,061 --> 00:33:44,820
I was unreliable before.

395
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:50,080
But this time...

396
00:33:50,080 --> 00:33:51,989
This time...

397
00:33:55,410 --> 00:34:01,480
All you do is apologize! What's the point of apologizing? If we didn't catch you, will you apologize to us?

398
00:34:07,610 --> 00:34:09,211
No, Xiaowen...

399
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:31,099
Where's Xiaowen?

400
00:34:31,099 --> 00:34:32,899
He left.

401
00:34:32,899 --> 00:34:37,200
How did you two do on the final exam?

402
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:40,060
None of your business. Take care of your own problems first.

403
00:34:57,460 --> 00:35:00,860
[Five-Year Past Exams and Three-Year Mock Exams (English)]

404
00:35:36,942 --> 00:35:43,090
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

405
00:35:43,090 --> 00:35:50,255
♫ It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine ♫

406
00:35:50,255 --> 00:35:56,345
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

407
00:35:56,345 --> 00:36:02,420
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

408
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:08,930
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

409
00:36:08,930 --> 00:36:14,677
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

410
00:36:14,677 --> 00:36:18,590
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

411
00:36:18,590 --> 00:36:22,012
♫  Let set sail on our dreams  ♫

412
00:36:22,012 --> 00:36:25,307
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

413
00:36:25,307 --> 00:36:31,967
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

414
00:36:31,967 --> 00:36:35,278
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

415
00:36:35,278 --> 00:36:39,490
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

416
00:36:39,490 --> 00:36:43,310
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

417
00:36:43,310 --> 00:36:51,070
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
